title: 136 - Should We Be Worried About Mitt?
description: On today's show, the boys welcome back one of the biggest dope heads around, Sales Guy Downtown BRAHN for a feel good Friday episode to send you into the weekend. Mitt is starting to worry everyone after leaving a hot dog in the air fryer for 45+ minutes and almost burning down the office, the boys give some updates on what they've been watching as of late, and answer some questions from the Pod FOD before making way for a rendition of Friday Bangerz curated by Gumpy to send you into the weekend. Don't forget to subscribe to the Youtube channel to watch full episodes, and submit your questions to @ThePodPMI on Twitter and Instagram. Have a great weekend, we'll see you Wednesday.
